^ Sachdev, Ameet; David Savage (November 3, 2009). "Mutual fund fee case tests what is a reasonable charge". Chicago Tribune. p. 19.  |access-date= requires |url= (help)
^ Sachdev, Ameet; David Savage (November 3, 2009). "Mutual fund fee case tests what is a reasonable charge". Chicago Tribune. p. 19.  |access-date= requires |url= (help)
