California SB1: Road Repair & Accountability Act of 2017 Updates


The Road Repair and Accountability Act of 2017 (SB1), provides funding to allow California’s transportation agencies to make a real dent in the $78 billion shortfall for needed repairs on local roads and streets. Stay up-to-date on SB1 as program guidelines are developed and how to focus your funding efforts.








